              ]
            },
            "id": "startAndCompleteQuest",
            "type": "genericAction"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "outro2",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNext",
              "text": "I'm glad you understand what I've told you but... did you know? Based on your current level, you won't be able to face the Black Mage. Heck you won't be able to face off his disciple's slave's monster's pet's dummy! Are you sure you are ready to protect Maple World like that?"
            },
            "id": "outro1",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "outro1",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "outro3",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "text": "You may be a member of the Cygnus Knights, but that doesn't mean you're a knight. Forget being the official knight. You're not even a Knight-in-Training, yet. A lot of time will pass where you will just sit around here, doing paperwork for the Cygnus Knights, but..."
            },
            "id": "outro2",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "outro2",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": "outro4",
                  "text": "Next"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendNextPrev",
              "text": "But then again, no one is born strong, anyway. The Empress also prefers that she creates an enviroment where a string of powerful knights can be nurtured and created, as opposed to finding a supernaturally-gifted knight. For now, you'll have to become a Knight-in-Training, and make yourself much more powerful so you'll become useful later on. We'll talk about the duties of being a Cygnus Knight once you reach that level of competency."
            },
            "id": "outro3",
            "type": "dialogue"
          },
          {
            "dialogue": {
              "choices": [
                {
                  "nextState": "outro3",
                  "text": "Previous"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Ok"
                },
                {
                  "nextState": null,
                  "text": "Exit"
                }
              ],
              "dialogueType": "sendPrev",
              "text": "Take the portal on the left side and go straight, and you'll head towards #b Training Forest I # . There, you'll find the training instructor for the Knights, Kiku. The next time I see you, I'd like for you to be atleast at level 10."
            },
            "id": "outro4",
            "type": "dialogue"
          }
        ]
      }
